		{
			"id": "http://curt.micro.blog/2017/08/18/brawling-with-bandannaclad.html",
	      	
			"content_html": "<p>“Brawling with bandanna-clad antifas may seem romantic to some disaffected young men, but being mocked by clowns? Probably not so much.” —<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2017/08/17/opinion/how-to-make-fun-of-nazis.html?smprod=nytcore-ipad&amp;smid=nytcore-ipad-share\">Moises Velasquez-Manoff</a></p>\n",
