		},
		
		{
			"id": "http://curt.micro.blog/2017/08/18/it-is-not.html",
	      	
			"content_html": "<p>“it is not possible for a Cabinet officer or White House staffer to comfort himself or herself that ‘at least the president’s heart is good.’ … Trump has opened his own chest for all to see. And the cavity is horrifyingly empty.” —<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/there-is-a-shriveled-emptiness-where-trumps-soul-once-resided/2017/08/17/bb9edd22-8370-11e7-b359-15a3617c767b_story.html\">Michael Gerson</a></p>\n",
